events.text: RAAAH! I've had enough of you and your nonsense! Now perish within my hands!
Come on, come on, t-think of something... Think! This can't be the end for me-
AHA! Finally! My madness reached its peak condition! Time to finish this.
Hey you! You think I'm in for a losing battle!? There's one more trick up my sleeve!
EAT THIS!
H-hey stop that! What is this!?
It hurts! RAAAAAAAA-
And it looks like the cat got the mouse... What do you have to say for yourself?
H-hey don't even think about it, y-you! Y-you! You idiot!
And to think I was thinking and willing to give you another chance.
Chance? What are you talking about?
I still remember the time I had with you before you were dealt with.
You were a nuisance, a headache, and I had to get rid of you for my safety.
But was burying me in my own grave necessary!? I laid there for years!
I felt rage energy coming inside me! Why do you think I was driven to do all this!?
...No matter now. I have thought of trying again, trying again with you eventually. Reconnecting.
But you just proved to me that you're not worth it. Unforgivable.
...Unforgivable, of course you say it.
You destroyed my home! How could I forgive you!? You may be my son, but I denounce you from the title!
N-now now... D-don't murder me with hatchets and whatnot-
I already did it once! And I'll do it again!
W-WAIT WAIT STOP NO-
